    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Institutional forms that function under a system of rules to achieve some goal and that maintain a technical and material organization, constitutions, staff, etc., and that joins members that share citizenship of one nation, and some common interest. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
